<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.2.8">
<l>tīvāyval viṉaiyā ruṭaṉiṉṟuci ṟantavarpōl</l>
<l>mēvāven narakat tiṭavuṟṟuvi raintuvantār</l>
<l>mūvāvā ṉavartam mutalvāmati kōḷviṭutta</l>
<l>tēvāniṉ ṉaṭaintēṉ tiruviṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My wicked, fiery-mouthed sins, staying with [me] like relatives,</l>
<l>Came rushing, reaching to cast me into uninhabitable, burning hell;</l>
<l>First of the ageless celestials, god who split the serpent of the moon,</l>
<l>I take refuge in you, the one who dwells in Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
